TextCell[Row[List[\"TTeXShow[\", Style[\"ID\", Bold], \"] returns a TeX \
string for the components of the tensor object \", Style[\"ID\", Bold], \" in \
its default index configuration and coordinate system.\\nTTeXShow[\", \
