simplifies them, before they are converted to TeX. \", Style[\"rules\", \
Bold], \" can be either a single rule of the form \", Style[\"lhs \\[Rule] \
rhs\", Bold], \" or a list of rules.\\nTTeXShow[\", Style[\"ID\", Bold], \", \
