example, {x \\[Rule] r Sin[\\[Theta]] Cos[\\[Phi]], y \\[Rule] r \
Sin[\\[Theta]] Sin[\\[Phi]], z \\[Rule] r Cos[\\[Theta]]} is a transformation \
from Cartesian to spherical coordinates.\"]]]]\)", "Documentation" -> None, 
